Format 35
Input scrclass.inc
Input numreport.inc

Sides                   2
PageStyle               Headings

NoStyle Abstract


Style Chapter
	LabelString          "\thechapter"
	TocLevel 0
End


Style Bibliography
	TopSep                4
	LabelString           "Bibliography"
	LabelFont
	  Series              Bold
	  Size                Largest
	EndFont
End

